{"id":133197,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/简讯：布莱尔说为伊战死亡懊悔/","date":"2011-01-22T06:40:44Z","modified":"2011-01-22T06:40:44Z","title":"简讯：布莱尔说为伊战死亡懊悔","content":"<div>\n<p>英国前首相布莱尔出席伊拉克战争听证会时说他为2003年入侵伊拉克战争以及随后“造成的死亡感到懊悔”。</p>\n<p>布莱尔在长达4个小时的听证过程中敦促西方停止为对伊拉克采取的行动道歉，并且警告伊朗造成的威胁。</p>\n<p>他被问到是否伊拉克的现状加剧了伊朗和其他国家发展核武器的风险，布莱尔作出否定的回答。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/5pG6FwsXhpdIoxEZ6lncHIoFIOs/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/5pG6FwsXhpdIoxEZ6lncHIoFIOs/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/5pG6FwsXhpdIoxEZ6lncHIoFIOs/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/5pG6FwsXhpdIoxEZ6lncHIoFIOs/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=-rY8y0G5buE:bxeiPk1r-Jg:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=-rY8y0G5buE:bxeiPk1r-Jg:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=-rY8y0G5buE:bxeiPk1r-Jg:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=-rY8y0G5buE:bxeiPk1r-Jg:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=-rY8y0G5buE:bxeiPk1r-Jg:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=-rY8y0G5buE:bxeiPk1r-Jg:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/-rY8y0G5buE\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<h4>要翻墙? <a href=\"http://9293.biz\">用赛风</a>.</h4>\n","author":176,"cate